### ========== VARIÁVEIS ==========
@baseUrl = http://localhost:80
@token = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========== HEALTH ==========

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health

### ========== AUTH ==========

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@autodoc.local",
  "password": "changeme"
}

### Meus dados
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== DOCUMENTOS ==========

### Upload de PDF (multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./exemplo.pdf
------FormBoundary--

### Listar documentos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar com filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents?status=completed&type=pdf&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar documento por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enriquecer com XML
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/DOCUMENT_ID_AQUI/enrich
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----XmlBoundary

------XmlBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="xml"; filename="enriquecimento.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

< ./exemplo.xml
------XmlBoundary--

### ========== RELATÓRIOS ==========

### Sumário geral
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sumário por período
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/summary?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar documentos (relatório)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/documents?status=completed&page=1&page_size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== USUÁRIOS (admin only) ==========

### Listar usuários
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operador@autodoc.local",
  "name": "Operador Exemplo",
  "password": "senha123",
  "role": "operator"
}

### Atualizar usuário
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/USER_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Operador Atualizado",
  "role": "manager",
  "active": true
}

### Deletar usuário
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/USER_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
